# JDK 25 for Project Panama (Foreign Function & Memory API, finalized in JDK 22).
# Panama replaces JNI for calling native libraries from JVM — see docs/architecture/backend-graphics-strategy.md.
# Install with: sdk install java 25.0.2-zulu
# Or via coursier: cs java --jvm zulu:25.0.2 -- -version
java=25.0.2-zulu
